<subSubSection pageId="14" pageNumber="15" type="discussion">
<paragraph blockId="14.[264,1324,284,950]" pageId="14" pageNumber="15">
<emphasis box="[312,414,844,869]" italics="true" pageId="14" pageNumber="15">Remarks</emphasis>
: 
<taxonomicName box="[431,563,844,869]" class="Insecta" family="Cicadellidae" genus="Varta" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="14" pageNumber="15" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="japonica">
<emphasis box="[431,563,844,869]" italics="true" pageId="14" pageNumber="15">V. japonica</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
is closely related to 
<taxonomicName box="[814,987,844,869]" class="Insecta" family="Cicadellidae" genus="Varta" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="14" pageNumber="15" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="rubrostriata">
<emphasis box="[814,987,844,869]" italics="true" pageId="14" pageNumber="15">V. rubrostriata</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
but differs in having longer more slender ventral pygophore processes and longer aedeagal shaft having a narrow based ventro­apical process.
</paragraph>
